2 exercises I like doing for 🍑strength 😜

Hip Thrusts> yesterday we went for a strength, but I do like to mix it up and add volume also. 
We did 6x6 
🔥In between we did the Glute Ham Raise  6x10

Then Lunges we did 6x8 (4ea)
🔥In between we did hanging leg raises 6x10 (I used my elbow straps😂) 

Jumped into a class later, and did this WOD : 12 min AMRAP> 
10 pistol box jump overs
10 VUPs 

Nice little finisher 🦵🏽😂🔥 

let me know if you like these I’ll share more of my workouts 😏❤️
